# Introduction

This is a library for producing html reports from ShiftLeft Scan or AppThreat scan results

## Installation

```bash
pip install shiftleft-scan-reports
```

```bash
slreporter -a <app_name> -o <Output>
```
info.name: shiftleft-scan-reports
info.summary: Library for producing SARIF & html reports from ShiftLeft or AppThreat scan results
